# Library Management System

## Project Overview
A Java-based Library Management System developed using Java Swing and MySQL.

## Features
- Login System
- Dashboard
- Add Books
- Search Books
- Issue Books
- Return Books

## Technologies Used
- Java
- Java Swing
- MySQL
- JDBC

## Installation
1. Clone the repository
2. Open in VS Code/Eclipse
3. Configure MySQL Database
4. Run LoginPage.java

